OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cold and rather bright start.
OL,6,FBecoming increasingly cloudy through
OL,7,Fthe morning as occasional showers
OL,8,Fspread west, some may turn heavy in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers gradually easing this
OL,12,Fevening with partly cloudy skies.
OL,13,FCloudier for a time overnight with a
OL,14,Fchance of some outbreaks of light rain
OL,15,For drizzle. Becoming breezy and chilly.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA dry and sunny day with only
OL,18,Fa little patchy cloud. Becoming
OL,19,Fincreasingly breezy, particularly over
OL,20,Fhills. Turning cloudy overnight from
OL,21,Fthe east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
