OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,Fbut cloudy each day from Wednesday to
OL,7,FFriday, though increasingly sunny each
OL,8,Fafternoon as cloud burns back to
OL,9,Fcoasts. Breezy, particularly over
OL,10,Fhills. Rather cool, especially near
OL,11,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
